{"ID":270199, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"199\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs198.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs200.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 199<\/div>\n  <p class=\"cont\">cannot obtain the blessings by pursuing any other course except the way marked out by the Lord.\n  What if we should attempt to get the gift of the Holy Ghost through any other means<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> except the\n  signs or way which God hath appointed&mdash;would we obtain it? Certainly not; all other means\n  would fail. The Lord says do so and so, and I will bless you.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">Key Words of the Priesthood<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">There are certain key words<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span> and signs<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span> belonging to the Priesthood which must be observed\n  in order to obtain the blessing.<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span> The sign of Peter was to repent and be baptized for the remission\n  of sins, with the promise of the gift of the Holy Ghost;<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span> and in no other way is the gift of the Holy\n  Ghost obtained.<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span><\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">Difference Between the Holy Ghost and the Gift of the Holy Ghost<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">There is a difference between the Holy Ghost and the gift of the Holy Ghost. Cornelius<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span>\n  received the Holy Ghost before he was baptized, which was the convincing power of God<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span> unto him\n  of the truth of the Gospel,<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span> but he could not receive the gift of the Holy Ghost until after he was\n  baptized. Had he not taken this sign or ordinance upon him, the Holy Ghost which convinced him\n  of the truth of God,<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span> would have left him. Until he obeyed these ordinances and received the gift\n  of the Holy Ghost,<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span> by the laying on of hands,<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span> according to the order of God,<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span> he could not have\n  healed the sick or commanded an evil spirit to come out of a man, and it obey him; for the spirits\n  might say unto him, as they did to the sons of Sceva: &ldquo;Paul we know and Jesus we know, but who\n  are ye?&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">14<\/span> It mattereth not whether we live long or short<span class=\"footRef\">15<\/span> on the earth after we come to a knowledge\n  of these principles and obey them unto the end.<span class=\"footRef\">16<\/span> I know that all men will be damned if they do not\n  come in the way<span class=\"footRef\">17<\/span> which He hath opened, and this is the way marked out by the word of the Lord.<span class=\"footRef\">18<\/span><\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">The Universal Resurrection<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">As concerning the resurrection, I will merely say that all men will come from the grave as they\n  lie down, whether old or young; there will not be &ldquo;added unto their stature one cubit,&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">19<\/span> neither taken\n  from it; all will be raised by the power of God,<span class=\"footRef\">20<\/span><\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109036\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109036)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109036)\">Acts 8:14-20<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116248\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116248)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116248)\">D&amp;C 130:11<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106110\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106110)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106110)\">Ex. 4:28<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108890\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108890)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108890)\">John 20:30<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116271\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116271)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116271)\">D&amp;C 130:20-21<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108943\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108943)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108943)\">Acts 2:37-38<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113941\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113941)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113941)\">D&amp;C 49:11-14<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109037\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109037)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109037)\">Acts 8:14-20<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109068\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109068)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109068)\">Acts 10:44-48<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">7. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109056\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109056)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109056)\">Acts 10:1<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">8. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112403\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112403)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112403)\">Alma 62:45<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112732\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112732)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112732)\">3 Ne. 28:29<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113215\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113215)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113215)\">D&amp;C 11:21<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114973\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114973)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114973)\">D&amp;C 90:10<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">9. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109725\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109725)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109725)\">Gal. 2:5,14<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109885\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109885)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109885)\">Col. 1:5<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116567\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116567)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116567)\">D&amp;C 135:7<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">10. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109395\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109395)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109395)\">Rom. 15:8<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111294\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111294)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111294)\">2 Ne. 28:28<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">11. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109069\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109069)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109069)\">Acts 10:44-48<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">12. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109041\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109041)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109041)\">Acts 8:18<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113585\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113585)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113585)\">D&amp;C 33:15<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113611\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113611)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113611)\">D&amp;C 35:6<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113945\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113945)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113945)\">D&amp;C 49:14<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"117192\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 117192)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(117192)\">A of F 1:4<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111818\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111818)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111818)\">Alma 6:1<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112472\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112472)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112472)\">Hel. 8:18<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114624\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114624)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114624)\">D&amp;C 84:18<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109164\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109164)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109164)\">Acts 19:15<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108125\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108125)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108125)\">Matt. 20:1-16<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111067\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111067)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111067)\">1 Ne. 22:31<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111578\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111578)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111578)\">Mosiah 5:8<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">17. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108474\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108474)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108474)\">Luke 7:30<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108525\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108525)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108525)\">Luke 13:24<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113971\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113971)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113971)\">D&amp;C 50:17-20<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">18. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106022\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106022)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106022)\">Gen. 15:1<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109046\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109046)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109046)\">Acts 8:25<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110910\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110910)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110910)\">1 Ne. 2:3<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114701\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114701)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114701)\">D&amp;C 84:45<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116873\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116873)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116873)\">Moses 7:13<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n   